Terrifying dashcam footage has emerged of cars enveloped by a raging wildfire on a road in eastern Siberia - with one vehicle driving around in the road and turning back in a desperate bid to escape the inferno .
At the start visibility for the driver of the car with the dashcam is zero , then intense blue flames from burning trees .
Wildfires in Siberia have been raging since March 19 , with the death toll this week climbing to 30 and 500 injured .